19:36.259 --> 19:39.126
Oh, boy.
This system is very complex.

19:39.220 --> 19:41.506
/ need hardline access.
What's the problem?

19:41.598 --> 19:44.260
Newcy's never
been uploaded
to a ship's OS.

19:44.351 --> 19:46.888
Without the proper
admin rights, she could
be ovenNritten.

19:47.020 --> 19:48.510
She'd get lost in
the command line.

19:48.605 --> 19:50.937
I want to do it, Johnny.
For you.

19:51.024 --> 19:53.811
Okay. Love you, Newce.
Go get 'em.

19:54.694 --> 19:56.104
I got your message, Zeph.

19:57.072 --> 19:59.063
What's the big
excitement?

19:59.199 --> 20:01.781
Oh, Fancy.
Do I know you?

20:01.951 --> 20:03.202
Oh, uh, around.

20:03.286 --> 20:05.197
So where's this gear
you told me about?

20:05.288 --> 20:06.528
What? Oh, yes.

20:06.623 --> 20:10.536
Uh,lasked
this nice company
officer to come identify

20:10.627 --> 20:13.960
some lab equipment
I boughtwhich may be
