Okay, we just did this.
Who are you?

20:33.316 --> 20:36.023
What about who are you?
Well, I'm...

20:38.029 --> 20:39.109
l'm...

20:42.158 --> 20:43.694
Hold on.
(CHUCKLES)

20:44.202 --> 20:45.237
Okay.

20:45.912 --> 20:47.743
Based on the samples I got
from the Black Root ship,

20:47.831 --> 20:50.493
