And now, I can too.

20:59.008 --> 21:01.135
Well, the wiping part,
at least.

21:01.219 --> 21:02.709
Do you know what
this means, Pree?

21:02.804 --> 21:04.669
Am I a scientist too?

21:05.432 --> 21:06.797
That would make sense.

21:06.891 --> 21:08.301
lfeel smart.

21:09.686 --> 21:11.472
She can't control us anymore.

21:11.563 --> 21:15.181
Well, that is something
to get excited about.

21:15.442 --> 21:19.060
So I guess now we just
have to figure out what
to do with it.

21:20.196 --> 21:22.653
