knew what we were doing?

21:30.248 --> 21:32.830
Those bush-herders?
Not even close.

21:33.460 --> 21:34.916
You were
a natural, Jaq.

21:35.003 --> 21:37.164
Tickets for two people.

21:37.964 --> 21:40.250
Hold this.
WOMAN: That won't
be possible.

21:40.383 --> 21:42.499
Word is no one's allowed
on Westerley these days.

21:42.594 --> 21:44.255
Closest I can
get you is Leith.

21:45.138 --> 21:47.504
